# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Frontend (Web) – copy to .env.local and fill in. For production, set in your host (e.g. Vercel).
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Vite only exposes variables that start with VITE_. They are inlined at build time.

# Deployed backend (API) URL. Leave unset in dev so the app uses the Vite proxy (/api → localhost:3001).
# Production: set to your API origin including /api if your API is mounted at /api, or the full base URL.
# Examples:
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-api.up.railway.app/api
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-api.onrender.com/api

# VITE_API_URL=

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Stripe – Pro checkout. Publishable key from Stripe Dashboard (safe to expose).
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# VITE_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_live_...

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Ads (free users only). Optional; leave unset to show no ads.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Google AdSense: create an account at google.com/adsense, add a display ad unit, then set:
# VITE_ADSENSE_CLIENT_ID=ca-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
# VITE_ADSENSE_SLOT_ID=XXXXXXXXXX

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# About page – donation links (optional). If set, buttons appear on the About page.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# VITE_DONATION_KOFI_URL=https://ko-fi.com/felipecunha23777
# VITE_DONATION_GITHUB_SPONSORS_URL=https://github.com/sponsors/yourname
